column5: Hi all. I was out on Bellwood lake today. I would of put us on the board but diddnt take  a tape measure. Only around a 2ft snot rocket but still. We got about 5 total. one had to come home as he took the hook to deep and was bleeding like a stuck pig. I gotta get my wife to down load pictures next time. Colin.  p.s. we need a team name. ( im not good at making stuff up)
You might of posted in the wrong spot.  Nice catches.
